<li id="cite_note-105"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-105">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Camus1947"><span class="ouvrage" id="Albert_Camus1947">Albert Camus, <cite class="italique">La peste</cite> (livre numérique), Gallimard, Paris, <time>1947</time>, 314&#160;<abbr class="abbr" title="pages">p.</abbr> <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Sp%C3%A9cial:Ouvrages_de_r%C3%A9f%C3%A9rence/2-291-08655-3" title="Spécial:Ouvrages de référence/2-291-08655-3"><span class="nowrap">2-291-08655-3</span></a> et <a href="/wiki/Sp%C3%A9cial:Ouvrages_de_r%C3%A9f%C3%A9rence/9782291086550" title="Spécial:Ouvrages de référence/9782291086550"><span class="nowrap">9782291086550</span></a>, <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a>&#160;<span class="plainlinks noarchive nowrap"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://worldcat.org/oclc/1143616862&amp;lang=fr">1143616862</a></span>, notice <a href="/wiki/Biblioth%C3%A8que_nationale_de_France" title="Bibliothèque nationale de France">BnF</a> <abbr class="abbr" title="numéro">n<sup>o</sup></abbr>&#160;<span class="plainlinks noarchive nowrap"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://catalogue.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/cb32939582j.public">FRBNF32939582</a></span>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/albertcamus-lapeste-1947/page/n311/mode/2up">présentation en ligne</a>)</small>, <abbr class="abbr" title="page(s)">p.</abbr>&#160;312<span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=La+peste&amp;rft.pub=Gallimard%2C+Paris&amp;rft.aulast=Camus&amp;rft.aufirst=Albert&amp;rft.date=1947&amp;rft.pages=312&amp;rft.tpages=314&amp;rft.isbn=2-291-08655-3&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F114