_Corcuff" title="Philippe Corcuff">Philippe Corcuff</a></span>&#160;• <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mikha%C3%AFl_W._Ramseier" title="Mikhaïl W. Ramseier">Mikhaïl W. Ramseier</a></span></td>
